title: Jeff Caudill from Gameface
itunes:title: Jeff Caudill from Gameface
description:
If you need to feel good today, listen to a little Gameface. Then, come back here and listen to this great chat with the frontman of said band, Jeff Caudill. We go into his extensive experience in the Orange County hardcore and punk scene, his design work and finding positivity in the midst of darkness. I loved this discussion and think you will to.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
